    <string name="about">About Quick Diary</string>
    <string name="about_content">Quick Diary is a minimal daily journal app designed to help you capture your thoughts, feelings, and experiences.\n\nFeatures:\n• Simple and intuitive interface\n• Daily mood tracking\n• Writing prompts to spark inspiration\n• Calendar view to navigate your entries\n• Secure PIN protection\n• Export and backup your entries\n• Timeline view to browse past entries\n\nQuick Diary is built with privacy in mind. All your data is stored locally on your device, and you have full control over your information.</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_content">Privacy Policy\n\nLast Updated: January 2026\n\nAt Quick Diary, we take your privacy seriously. This privacy policy explains how we handle your data.\n\nData Storage\n• All your diary entries, moods, and app data are stored locally on your device\n• We do not collect, transmit, or store any of your personal information on external servers\n• Your data never leaves your device unless you explicitly choose to export or backup it\n\nNo Internet Connection Required\n• Quick Diary works completely offline\n• We do not require an internet connection to function\n• This ensures your private thoughts remain private\n\nNo Tracking or Analytics\n• We do not use any analytics, tracking, or advertising services\n• We do not collect usage statistics or user behavior data\n• Your app usage remains completely private\n\nExport and Backup\n• Export and backup features are optional and only work when you explicitly choose to use them\n• You have full control over when and where your data is exported\n• Exported files are created only on your device or in locations you specify\n\nData Deletion\n• You can delete all your data at any time from the Settings menu\n• Deletion is permanent and cannot be undone\n• We do not retain any copies of your deleted data\n\nThird-Party Services\n• Quick Diary does not integrate with any third-party services\n• We do not share your data with any external parties\n• Your information remains exclusively on your device\n\nChanges to This Policy\n• We may update this privacy policy from time to time\n• Any changes will be reflected in the app\n• Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy\n\nContact\n• If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please review the app settings\n\nYour privacy is our priority. Quick Diary is designed to be a safe space for your thoughts and reflections.</string>
    
